data.description: Like new in Mountain Vail Estates! This stunning home built in 2016 is dressed to impress with so many upgrades! This 4 bedroom, 2 bath home has 2155 sq ft that sits in a split floorplan. The open concept kitchen has sparkling granite countertops with large island, tastefully done backsplash, stainless steel appliances with wall dual oven plus huge walk-in pantry. The master suite has dual vanities with granite countertops plus shower/tub combo and a spacious walk-in closet. The lot is North/South facing with landscaping already complete in front and back yards and is directly across from a recreational/park area. perfect for kids and animals. This home is sure to please the pickiest buyer with all the gorgeous detail.
